Broader credit access

08/06/2022

Key takeaway: Upstart model leads to broder credit access for invisible primes. There are losers as well.

3 Who benefits?

3.1 Borrower characteristics

r <- list()

r[[1]] <- felm(rejected_trad~I(fico_score/100)+factor(incomelt50)+factor(education_level2)+factor(salaried)+thinfile|zip_year|0|zip_code,data=loans)
r[[2]] <- felm(rejected_trad~lowfico*factor(incomelt50)+lowfico*factor(education_level2)+lowfico*factor(salaried)+lowfico*thinfile|zip_year|0|zip_code,data=loans)
r[[3]] <- felm(I(aprdiff)~I(fico_score/100)+factor(incomelt50)+factor(education_level2)+factor(salaried)+thinfile|zip_year|0|zip_code,data=loans)
